Mereka hanya keluar di malam hari,

92
00:09:35,868 --> 00:09:38,370
jadi aku tidak bisa beristirahat.

93
00:09:39,538 --> 00:09:42,291
Aku menemukan bau baru di dekat sini.

94
00:09:43,292 --> 00:09:45,502
Mereka pasti ada di sekitar sini.

95
00:09:46,420 --> 00:09:47,713
Mereka?

96
00:09:48,672 --> 00:09:49,882
Mungkinkah...

97
00:09:50,382 --> 00:09:51,758
